---
title: Mexican Chicken & Cheesy Corn Chip Crunch Bowl with Avocado & Roast Tomato Salsa
description: Who needs takeout when you can whip up this fiesta in a bowl right at home? Juicy Mexican-spiced chicken teams up with crunchy corn chips for the ultimate texture combo, while creamy avocado and zesty roast tomato salsa bring the flavour party. It’s everything you love about Mexican cuisine, reimagined for your dinner table—no delivery fee required!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
